This is a Toolkit App built with Tauri + Shadcn Svelte + TailwindCSS v4

# Component Preferences
- Svelte version is v5, please use Runes
- Use shadcn-svelte components: Button, Card, Input, Label, Popover, Switch, Tabs, Textarea.
- Style exclusively with Tailwind CSS v4 (avoid `<style>` tags).
- Use @lucide/svelte for icons